content.html: The $1,300 Calcifer sweater made a WILD decision with where to put his eyes
content.value: The $1,300 Calcifer sweater made a WILD decision with where to put his eyes

photo.alt: An Asian model with black sunglasses looks straight ahead at us. She's wearing fuzzy, long-sleeved sweater color blocked in white, yellow, orange, and red to look like flame. On the chest are hand-sewn embroidery of white eyes with black dots that look unfortunately similar to nipples.
A Black model lays down, one hand touching her impassive face, with the other hand clutching a black leather purse printed with Calcifer on it. She wears a matching Calcifer sweater.
